  "texts": [
    "In general papers, it has been noted that ChatGPT tends to 1) use the same style and expressions repeatedly, 2)",
    "show a decrease in the frequency of basic verbs like 'is' and 'are,' and 3) frequently use adjectives and adverbs.",
    "Particularly for adjectives and adverbs, numerous words that ChatGPT frequently uses have been pointed out.",
    "Because this study only counted the records where specific words or phrases occurred, it did not evaluate the weight of terms appearing multiple times.",
    "In the current study, several words that were previously identified as frequently used by ChatGPT did not exhibit a notable increase in usage; yet, ChatGPT may actually overuse these words more than suggested by the results of this study."
  ]
}